{"tid":1930673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[美國要派錢了] 侵侵要每人派一千蚊一個月","createTime":"2020-03-17T17:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T00:54:45.000Z","uid":130105,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"be3164b9c292b4c4646bc62b8a3179413f7b573a","tid":1930673,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:03:47.000Z","msg":"美國又抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=====================<br />\n&bull;President Trump wants to send cash to Americans suffering financially from the coronavirus crisis immediately <br />\n&bull;'Americans need cash now and the president wants to give cash now,' Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin said Tuesday in the press briefing room '<br />\n&bull;Mnuchin said he was previewing the plan to Capitol Hill Republicans and then would provide more details<br />\n&bull;Sen. Mitt Romney, a Utah Republican, floated a universal basic income-like stimulus of $1,000 a month during the outbreak <br />\n&bull;Former Democratic presidential candidate Andrew Yang centered his career on the concept of providing Americans with a universal basic income <br />\n&bull;Coronavirus symptoms: what are they and should you see a doctor?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/03/17/16/26079260-8122293-image-a-2_1584461879830.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F03%2F17%2F16%2F26079260-8122293-image-a-2_1584461879830.jpg&h=f441410f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n President Trump (left) and Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin (right) said Tuesday they wanted to send Americans checks to keep the economy going amid the coronavirus outbreak<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/03/17/16/26036636-8122293-Sen_Mitt_Romney_R_Utah_said_Monday_he_supports_giving_1_000_each-a-1_1584461602434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F03%2F17%2F16%2F26036636-8122293-Sen_Mitt_Romney_R_Utah_said_Monday_he_supports_giving_1_000_each-a-1_1584461602434.jpg&h=bca9b1c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Sen. Mitt Romney, R-Utah, said Monday he supports giving $1,000 each month to working Americans during the crisis<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/03/16/16/26036618-8117729-image-a-18_1584376648685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F03%2F16%2F16%2F26036618-8117729-image-a-18_1584376648685.jpg&h=be228757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Former Democratic presidential candidate Andrew Yang campaigned on giving $1,000 each month to every American<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8122293/Donald-Trump-wants-checks-Americans-IMMEDIATELY.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8122293%2FDonald-Trump-wants-checks-Americans-IMMEDIATELY.html&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzByPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=b0c15232\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8122293/Donald-Trump-wants-checks-Americans-IMMEDIATELY.html</a>"},{"pid":"12a015109e6cf085b1fc486490e5c7926389502a","tid":1930673,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:09:02.000Z","msg":"romney = 反trump socialist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c21a734aeef5f8ab14e90ac679c17d88800963","tid":1930673,"uid":214036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93476caf19ceb3dfd7f7381b74757e2e8bc66aa4","tid":1930673,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86c21a734aeef5f8ab14e90ac679c17d88800963","tid":193